title: Casas Nuevas Airport
text: Casas Nuevas Airport is an <a href="airstrip">airstrip</a> serving the city of <a href="Jiquilisco">Jiquilisco</a> in <a href="Usulut%C3%A1n%20Department">Usulután Department</a>, <a href="El%20Salvador">El Salvador</a>. The unmarked grass runway is east of the city.
